parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is on
the airbag does not deploy in a crash
the side curtain airbag deploys without a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The spontaneous deployment of an airbag can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag deploys without a crash
the side curtain airbag deploys without a crash
the airbag warning light is on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities if not addressed.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is on
the airbag warning light is intermittent
the side airbag off light is on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the manufacturer to provide replacement parts in a timely manner can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The part to repair the airbag recall is unavailable
the dealer does not have the part
the manufacturer does not provide an estimated date for the recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the low beam headlights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: The low beam headlights burn out frequently
sometimes while driving
leaving the driver with only high beams or no headlights at all. The bulbs may need to be replaced every few months
and the failure can occur on both sides of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power window master switch can cause the window to malfunction, leading to safety risks, such as difficulty escaping in an emergency.
symptoms: The window may not roll up or down
the switch may melt or overheat
and there may be a burning smell.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: The headlights may burn out frequently
fail to illuminate
or have a short lifespan.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various safety risks, such as engine stalling, loss of power, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The electrical system may malfunction
causing issues with the engine
lights
or other components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause serious safety risks, including increased risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light may come on
or the airbags may not deploy properly in an accident.
